Program: Discovery
Title: Expanding the Milky Way
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrx2t
Last Broadcast Date: 05 March 1998
A journey to the centre of our galaxy using infrared light. The discovery of Sagittarius A star and what it may mean for our galaxy. Also in the programme, the diet that helps avoid bowel cancer and how B vitamins can help the heart. Presenter: Graham Easton.